text: Laraesima scutellaris is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1868. It is known from Argentina and Brazil.BioLib.cz - Laraesima scutellaris. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1868
title: Laraesima scutellaris
